Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.06,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成為遊戲製作人應該如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:35.70,Other3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(584,358)}神田空太{\c&H000000&}：不 還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:35.70,Other3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HAA432F&\pos(630,494)}赤阪龍之介{\c&H000000&}：是嗎 那我就下線了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.70,Other3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[ 龍之介離開了聊天室 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:51.59,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找飼主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:51.59,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳情請詢問2-1神田空太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找飼主啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於想離開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫終於啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我吧 我幫你去那邊貼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想幫幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山遇到了什麼好事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飼主的事 我會幫你問問游泳部的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到想當飼主的人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為貓的飼主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要飼主的人是你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神 神田君 飼主是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話的意思是要幫助還沒習慣日本高中的椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 空太…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:43.22,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：「つきあう」有交往也有陪同的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這麼爽快就告白是鬧哪樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六有個想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼嘛 原來是這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正忙著找飼主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去拜託仁學長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田君 這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼好不好的 和我又沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 糟了 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 學弟也把衣服換了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內褲內褲！會帶著其他東西一起出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會非常在意的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的星期天鬧什麼啊鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白要和仁去約會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是約會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說了要去LoveHo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LoveHo？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love Hotel簡略成的那個LoveHo？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就是那個LoveHo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白被NTR了你也不在乎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:10:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去取材吧 有什麼好鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個土邦王仁學長去到旅館卻什麼都不做 這能想像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這方面來說肯定會開幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和新幹線到站時間那樣地準確
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學弟！ 換好衣服門口見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六十秒就準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十秒就給我搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚吃紅豆飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用找了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除限制！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把雙手的負重都扔掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是在做哪門子的修行…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是全力了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能變三次身呢 所以才說地球人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是外星人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應已經很近了 謹慎點接近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:18.81,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟蹤也請交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學弟 反應如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離真白大人還有十米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學弟 這是在取材嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著像是在約會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪學弟你太磨蹭了 你個懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說兩次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學弟 我已經受不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:18.56,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手 這樣會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為根本忍不住嘛 思念都快溢出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴露了要怎麼解釋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用「偶然碰到作戰」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢 神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼青山你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天育成班下課後就在這打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是那麼厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒哦 小七
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工服也很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起藏起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 上井草學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田君你太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得哪個好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這個更可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁想要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離得很近卻異常遙遠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 請給我這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像買了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我要回店裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息時間已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不說我也會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學弟 我的心好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種病會傳染嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像我也有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧椎名的工作並不是非我不可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁學長會不會是喜歡文靜漂亮的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始交往的風香也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼早就進行跟蹤了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在仁身邊的人總不是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 快阻止他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這是膝枕？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那語氣也表達得疼點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就閉嘴 膝枕也別隨便用 你在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規模真大啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 仁學長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說和預想的一樣 之後空太就交給你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和預想的一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說跟蹤他的事都露餡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等等 你理解現在的狀況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在孤男寡女在LoveHo裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要住這
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就沒明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好思考過再去行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和男人到這種地方來 要是發生了什麼的話該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:17:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒意義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管再怎麼想 我也只是出來取材的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了漫畫必須做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才來這的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太為什麼會在這
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓的飼主找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白的人是空太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人生是怎麼過來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫畫過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫畫過來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是在幹什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢 本來是準備給你打一拳的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反射性地出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁學長你現在在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OL留美小姐家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天請回櫻花莊去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 暫停吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都看不下去了 美咲學姐那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是給我說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲學姐為什麼不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要是回去就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是看到她沮喪的表情…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會格外地想侵犯她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說 比起我的事 真白那邊怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名的話 在睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡在空太的懷裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在床上睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鞋櫃和牆壁之間夾著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢 吵架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連吵架都算不上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是單方面地被即死連擊KO了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒有明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名真是非常荒唐 以我的常識根本不通用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對椎名來說 這些事都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪畫…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是畫漫畫才是她的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是沒有迷茫 總之就是很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真白說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到日本來是為了成為漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說“難得在繪畫的世界裡受到了肯定 真是太浪費了”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她卻說“我不需要”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個荒唐的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…多虧了這樣的椎名讓我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會以自己的意志去決定自己的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送別會會辦得隆重些的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:22:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白的人是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.96,0:23:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次和我說清楚的話 我會陪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人獎要加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要離開櫻花莊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.13,0:23:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的內褲的顏色…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:49.86,Title01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(664,450)\3c&H2AC5B1&}#04 變色的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 變態 問這麼色的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不准想像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.79,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一回目　毆れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:56.17,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}二回目って　どうだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:02:03.50,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}偶然じゃないよね　三回目が遭うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:07.05,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}変わった人だと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:10.56,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}割と皆いうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:17.71,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}気になったことは 違うんだ　そこじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:24.33,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}君は多分純粋で　純粋を負けず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:31.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}だから小さな日常にさえ　立ち向かって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:38.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢を持ってきた言葉じゃ　足りない夢にありが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:42.32,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}きっとこんな風に始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:45.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}新しいトキメキ世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:52.98,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢を持ってきた言葉を　知らないふりして行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:57.06,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}トキメキと夢のありか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}第一回 被人毆打
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:56.17,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}第二回又會如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:02:03.50,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}會有第三回絕對不是偶然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:07.05,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}真是個怪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:10.56,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}大家好像都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:17.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}應該在意的事不是那個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:24.33,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}你或許非常單純 並且不向單純低頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:31.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}所以即便是簡單的日常也會抵抗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:38.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}充滿著夢想的話語便是夢想不足的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:42.32,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一定是像這樣開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:45.87,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}那片嶄新的心跳世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:52.98,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}充滿著夢想的話語 就當作沒有聽過繼續前行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:57.06,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}走向那心跳與夢的所在
