Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.06,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}迷いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:55.59,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}涙をのみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:58.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}不器用だね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.79,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢も遠回り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:07.79,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}大空を見上げ何も言えず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:16.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}胸が痛む訳考えていた
