Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.67,0:22:20.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}風を走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:27.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}君と僕の仲で何が始まったのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:29.02,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:36.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}キメキラ光る太陽が照らす場所をずっと進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.81,0:22:42.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}永遠など　知らないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:37.35,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}給予了我所度過的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:46.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}必須在這裡刻下心靈吼叫的那一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:49.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}I am dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.06,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一直很迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:55.59,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}強忍著淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:58.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}真是不中用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}連夢想也與我無緣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:07.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}看著天空一句話也說不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:16.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一直思考著胸口的那股痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:17.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}DAYS of DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.67,0:22:20.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}追趕著清風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:27.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}你與我之間發生了什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:29.02,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}雖然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:36.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}向著那耀眼的太陽所照耀之處前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.81,0:22:42.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}永遠什麼的 我才不知道呢
